Download TIGER shapes for Metropolitan Divisions

Source: R/metropolitan_divisions.R
tt_metropolitan_divisions.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Metropolitan Divisions

Usage

tt_metropolitan_divisions(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_metropolitan_divisions()
